name: Metalife - Friends Checking Out Some Art
description:
Made this 3D abstract to show a little bit of metalife.  Gonna be going into the MV just to chill and do stuff.

The painting that the meta friends are in is a physical painting I made earlier this year, maybe last year.  I took a picture of it and changed it digitally to get a different look.

And the other painting is a digital painting I made this year.  Was gonna make it into an nft by itself.  And just ended up adding it to this nft.


🙂 🙂
